{"tid":1138611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宋慧喬畫煙燻妝！網驚：不是周子瑜？","createTime":"2019-05-04T15:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T04:38:47.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf75c5014c9f3f0f27c31c8ba8e62fbf8e9d48e","tid":1138611,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n現年36歲的南韓「國民女神」宋慧喬，1996年出道的她，已演戲22年，被外界形容根本像是「防腐劑美貌」，平常通常以淡妝現身的她，近日參加知名品牌服裝秀時，竟畫著濃妝亮相，罕見的造型讓粉絲眼睛一亮，更有網友指出畫著「煙燻妝」的宋慧喬，竟意外神似南韓女團TWICE成員周子瑜，引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/y18EndihcBoTEOov1Souwg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/04ba328aed1e071c494d23d14ddf2f0c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fy18EndihcBoTEOov1Souwg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F04ba328aed1e071c494d23d14ddf2f0c&h=1d83ae56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲宋慧喬平常都以淡妝亮相。（圖／翻攝自宋慧喬IG）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yA_dBEHGT_iIEefjLDbEaQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/9f5afe41f3cfa862fbc92c3efe1c0deb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyA_dBEHGT_iIEefjLDbEaQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F9f5afe41f3cfa862fbc92c3efe1c0deb&h=9799a275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宋慧喬日前遠赴美國參加知名品牌時尚大秀，只見她身穿一件香芋色洋裝，配上一條金色項鍊，相比其他女星，宋慧喬穿得相當保守，但獨特的氣質，讓女神一出場，便緊緊抓住眾人的目光，成為鎂光燈追逐的焦點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OI.HkFV07EmeMQTU7zwkhg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzcwO2g9NzE4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/1e44f1349829b26f493e51e6c9dd6f70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOI.HkFV07EmeMQTU7zwkhg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzcwO2g9NzE4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F1e44f1349829b26f493e51e6c9dd6f70&h=b6f82315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋慧喬現身美國看秀。（圖／翻攝自宋慧喬IG）<br />\n<br />\n更引人注目的是，平常總以淡妝示人的宋慧喬，這次罕見畫上煙燻妝，眼線以及眼妝用色相當大膽，再擦上深紅色的唇妝，看起來不僅女人味十足，更相當地有氣勢，女神獨特的造型風格，掀起熱議，更一舉登上微博熱搜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kJDwsbFrh6Aet7z6wX9nPg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9NTUx/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/a510b0534bef3dbfccb3666eb86e44d9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkJDwsbFrh6Aet7z6wX9nPg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQwO2g9NTUx%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fa510b0534bef3dbfccb3666eb86e44d9&h=32ab5180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲宋慧喬罕見畫上煙燻大濃妝。（圖／翻攝自新浪娛樂微博）<br />\n<br />\n對此，有網友認為宋慧喬不管什麼造型都美，「很少見她化濃妝，驚艷到了！」、「不一樣的美，還是好看的」，不過也有部分網友表坦言，這個妝容並不適合她，「第一眼真心沒認出來，感覺有點太成熟」、「還是淡妝看上去比較清純、清爽」，更值得注意的是，有網友指出濃妝版的宋慧喬，竟神似TWICE的台灣籍成員周子瑜，特別是眼睛以及鼻子的部分，2女神意外撞臉，讓粉絲直呼不可思議，意外掀起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DPPv.gOd3Vr_LM5HW2.C_Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/57d261b38888dbafeb4e4a8d33b5c974\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDPPv.gOd3Vr_LM5HW2.C_Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F57d261b38888dbafeb4e4a8d33b5c974&h=2132745a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋慧喬畫上煙燻妝竟意外撞臉周子瑜。（圖／翻攝自周子瑜、宋慧喬IG）"},{"pid":"e08386de2dcbf2a262307325697c453084bb5144","tid":1138611,"uid":138658,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"2個唔同級數 侮辱咗喬妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c2ef7d06cc439bd1eaa342bf073127ef751d9b","tid":1138611,"uid":43061,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"死台狗乜鳩都話周子瑜 吹撚完未呀<br />\n人地子瑜係都係中國人啦 洗撚你班台狗吹？"},{"pid":"eb2e9f9b3693e0beb749026d43a3bbbdbbeaf915","tid":1138611,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"31c2ef7d06cc439bd1eaa342bf073127ef751d9b","tid":1138611,"uid":43061,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"死台狗乜鳩都話周子瑜 吹撚完未呀<br />\n人地子瑜係都係中國人啦 洗撚你班台狗吹？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"請尊重！🇹🇼"},{"pid":"70fe81efcde37d5f3d4daa039d978e33edd77c67","tid":1138611,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:02:08.000Z","msg":"又真係有少少似嘅"},{"pid":"05eea7d115de7600577328cf6a5988a80df658e8","tid":1138611,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"好唔掂喎"}]}